Sentencas: La0.7Sr0.3Cu1-xFexO3-delta (LSCF) cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFC) have been prepared by conventional solid state reaction (SSR) and EDTA-citrate-nitrate complexing process (ECNP).
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.7Sr0.3Cu1-xFexO3-δ cathode materials

Sentencas: The samples prepared by ECNP exhibited higher electrical conductivity than those by SSR.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.7Sr0.3Cu1-xFexO3-δ cathode materials

Sentencas: AC impedance results measured at 700 degrees C indicated that polarization resistance was decreased with the addition of Fe, and it reached the minimum (2.51 Omega cm(2)) when x=0.6.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.7Sr0.3Cu1-xFexO3-δ cathode materials
